comments: Collins (ATL) and Crowder (MIA) both engage and disengage in arm contact during the rebound.
Young (ATL) makes contact to Adebayo's (MIA) arm during his shot attempt.
Iguodala (MIA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is taken.
Dragic (MIA) makes slight contact to Young's (ATL) arm as he gathers and enters his shooting motion.
Collins (ATL) makes marginal contact to the body of Adebayo (MIA) at the end of drive.
Adebayo (MIA) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Huerter (ATL) makes some contact to Adebayo's (MIA) arm during his follow-through.
Reddish (ATL) and Butler (MIA) engage and disengage in arm contact underneath the basket.
Butler (MIA) slightly brushes Young's (ATL) arm at the end of his drive.
Crowder (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Young (ATL) and  cleanly blocks the layup.
Adebayo (MIA) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Adebayo (MIA) is firming up and makes slight contact with Reddish (ATL) as they disengage during the pick.
Reddish (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position on Dragic (MIA) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Collins (ATL) briefly places both hands on Adebayo (MIA) prior to the inbound.
Adebayo (MIA) slightly extends his arms into Hunter (ATL) while setting the pick on the perimeter.
Young (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position on Adebayo (MIA) and cleanly dislodges the ball after he secures the rebound.
Crowder (MIA) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Adebayo (MIA) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
